item.title: Bridgestone - Reply All
item.description:
Bridgestone - Reply All
This Bridgestone Super Bowl ad wants you to imagine you've just accidentally hit "Reply All" instead of "Reply" on an email. Imagine it's one of those really personal emails that you only wanted one person to read. And now, imagine that everyone you've ever worked with is about to find out what you "really think." In this spot, you'll see just how far one man is willing to go to right his "Reply All" wrongs. "Like" this commercial on Facebook at www.facebook.com/BridgestoneTires
